  <metadata>
    <name>BCN-L2 — Costa Brava Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from BCN and ride into the Costa Brava. Hit Girona and Tossa de Mar Cliffs — 120m. Loop back to BCN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
